dct_title_s: Physical features of the contiguous United States / cartography by Tom Patterson.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading, gradient tints, and spot heights; depths shown by bathymetric tints. Shows mountains, plains, rivers, lakes, and ocean bathymetry. Elevations are in feet. State high points shown in bold. "May 17, 2020, version 1.01." Available on the Internet in electronic format.
